1113
01:13:13.579 --> 01:13:15.779
like a whistling. y'know I' saying.
to like. blend in.

1114
01:13:15.917 --> 01:13:17.317
No. Don't whistle.

1115
01:13:17.437 --> 01:13:19.670
No whistling. it's not the
Andy Griffith Show.

1116
01:13:19.679 --> 01:13:20.679
No whistling.

