1209
01:21:24.016 --> 01:21:24.916
- Shh.
- Shh.

1210
01:21:25.259 --> 01:21:26.259
-Shh!
-Shh!!

1211
01:21:29.158 --> 01:21:30.758
All right guys I'm here.

1212
