Dad!

1277
01:26:23.650 --> 01:26:25.750
Hank. No. no. Hank.

1278
01:26:27.397 --> 01:26:29.430
Hank. Listen. you're gonna be okay.

1279
01:26:29.514 --> 01:26:31.081
All right. you're gonna be just fine.

1280
